name: DiabetesMellitus
title: Diabetes Mellitus
description: OP-13 is the measure ID associated with the codes.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains ICD-10 codes associated with diabetes mellitus.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have diabetes mellitus.),(Inclusion Criteria: ICD-10 codes associated with diabetes mellitus.),(Exclusion Criteria: Values that are not related to diabetes mellitus, or those captured in systems other than ICD-10, are excluded from the value set.)
